<DocsPageSubtitle>
    When to use it
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    Use <Code Tag>BreakpointObserver</Code> when you want inline declarative rendering in markup. If you need to react in code-behind instead, inject <Code>IBreakpointService</Code> directly and use its <Code>Current</Code>, <Code>IsResolved</Code>, <Code>IsBelow</Code>, and <Code>IsAtLeast</Code> members.
</DocsPageParagraph>

